reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Extremely slow for Roblox game
reviews.reviewText: My child is a Roblox fanatic. That’s all she loves to play. To hear her constantly complain about how slow this gamer PC was became so draining. As a precaution, I scan the system files prior to downloading anything on the laptop, I do this with ALL computers and laptops I purchase. While doing a PC scan we discovered corrupted files. Big no-no for me. I was not expecting that from a brand new laptop. I sent it back for a refund. As of now the laptop has been received and is being processed. I didn’t have to pay for the return so that was why I rated it a 2. I guess I’ll have to save up a few more hundred for a top-tier laptop for her 🤷🏽‍♀️ For now, she’s back to taking over my MAC 🤦🏽‍♀️😡 It was in perfect condition from the outside view but had some things going on in the inside.
